{"tid":2122817,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民偷雞鼻離罩即屬違法  陳肇始：不排除擴大規管範圍","createTime":"2020-07-24T08:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T08:21:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"14591fd595fd25aeb8c300d64ab0f7ca677cc486","tid":2122817,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/UANTA2SK24ORKTOYZNG7UJ66F4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FUANTA2SK24ORKTOYZNG7UJ66F4%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Jvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=f90019e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FUANTA2SK24ORKTOYZNG7UJ66F4%2F&h=8f1aeef3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/UANTA2SK24ORKTOYZNG7UJ66F4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n市民偷雞鼻離罩即屬違法 <br />\n陳肇始：不排除擴大規管範圍<br />\n<br />\n法例第599I章規定任何人士於室內公眾地方均須佩戴口罩，違者最高會被罰款5,000元。法例生效首日，上班時間的紅磡隧道轉車站大排長龍，大部份市民都戴上口罩，惟有零星市民排隊時將口罩拉至下巴，也有從紅磡港鐵站天橋步行到轉車站的市民沒戴口罩，直至步入候車隊伍，又或發現攝錄機，才徐徐戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qYCoLkVPJrsRlLNcxViMvAKvbQ4=/190x142/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5Z3GQBCXG2SB5BT22TQXVLCH6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqYCoLkVPJrsRlLNcxViMvAKvbQ4%3D%2F190x142%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5Z3GQBCXG2SB5BT22TQXVLCH6Y.jpg&h=4a13e022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牛頭角街市有檔販將口罩拉至下巴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民轟政府「有事先做嘢」<br />\n<br />\n平日都會紅隧轉車站候車的Cyrus指，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一乘客黃先生表示，現時疫情越趨嚴重，。。。。。。。。。。。甚至將口罩令推廣至大街等室外公共場所。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n_-Dyxmz_Qe1HGdgN439BitNJrY=/190x142/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YYRIBH5MBRMEG7W7BGZRD4AXRI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn_-Dyxmz_Qe1HGdgN439BitNJrY%3D%2F190x142%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYYRIBH5MBRMEG7W7BGZRD4AXRI.jpg&h=cb99c296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有市民無視戴罩令，在人流眾多的紅隧巴士站拉低口罩。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者亦到牛頭角及九龍灣一帶的商場採訪，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，門庭若市的牛頭角街市，就有至少三、四名攤販將口罩拉至下巴。記者向其中一名將口罩拉下的魚販查詢，他隨即將口罩拉回鼻頭上，並指「𠵱家戴返啦」，旁邊的職員則連忙說：「我哋知㗎啦」，又表示「以後都會戴」。面對市民「半戴罩」，陳肇始表示按照相關規例，口罩需要完全覆蓋到口鼻，「個鼻凸出嚟，已經觸犯法例」。至於會否加辣擴大強制戴口罩範圍至戶內，她說大部份人都有在室外戴口罩，加上室外空氣較流通，彈性較大，如看到有人無戴口罩，市民可走開，但室內未必做到，且在戶外做運動等亦難以戴口罩。但她指當局會密切留意成效，不排除再增強制戴口罩的場所，包括戶外地方。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。至於昨日落實的室內公眾地方佩戴口罩法規則未有相關數字。"},{"pid":"1bb8c3b8e86a9eca2871ee11167c113266b590e7","tid":2122817,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"市民偷雞離罩即屬違法<br />\n咪姐係比個理由黑警 搶人口罩<br />\n易d入人罪姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0890562c0ec931aa9f7119273f65e896dc2dd19","tid":2122817,"uid":15010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:14:56.000Z","msg":"幾時完全封關呀<br />\n唔封關著到太空人咁岀街都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47d622a3e65bcd7d11126500c11617c78b78939","tid":2122817,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"林奠同班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16587c3ff43f5e731c81487ef7c33ed3b9f2911a","tid":2122817,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"商場保安指不清楚該處是否屬室內，稱要待上級的清晰指示。<br />\n<br />\n室內個定義跟控煙條例，控煙條例都行咗N咁多年啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7921c321610c1bf61973fa2e1d6c550f2de281","tid":2122817,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"咁個底褲口罩講幾吓咪就即刻犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55c3a8e1c126246f362ef50ca380c0ea01c9d05","tid":2122817,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:21:16.000Z","msg":"廢老: 口罩梗係用黎戴落口度, 唔通戴落鼻度"}]}